  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" />He who oppresses the poor shows contempt for his Maker,</para>
  <para style="q2">but he who is kind to the needy honours him.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" />The wicked is brought down in his calamity,</para>
