  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Sheol<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15:11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Sheol is the place of the dead.</char></note> and Abaddon are before the LORD—</para>
